{"word":"G4333 - προσεργάζομαι - prosergázomai - pros-er-gad'-zom-ahee - Gain","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">προσεργάζομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">prosergázomai</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">pros-er-gad'-zom-ahee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Gain</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - ஆதாயம் தேடு"},{"paragraph":"1. to work besides"},{"paragraph":"2. by working or trading to make or gain besides"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4314 - πρός - prós - pros/4314\">G4314</a> and <a href=\"#/G2038 - ἐργάζομαι - ergázomai - er-gad'-zom-ahee/2038\">G2038</a>; to <i>work additionally</i>, that is, (by implication) <i>acquire besides:</i> - gain.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}